                Matronis <lb n="2"/>Aufaniabus <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Pettronius <note>sic</note> Pat<lb break="no" n="4"/>roclus b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan> itera<lb break="no" n="5"/>ta statione <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ädikula mit der Darstellung dreier sitzender Matronen.</p>
            </div>
